<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="157" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="157">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="157">
Color pale yellow or yellowish white. Pronotum with three or four brown spots. Elytron with a brown-colored branched line pattern (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 5–8" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 5 - 8. Brachiacantha sp. 5 Brachiacantha bipartita, female 6 Brachiacantha aperta, female 7 Brachiacantha isthmena sp. nov. 8 Brachiacantha cachensis." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures5-8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520867" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">6</figureCitation>
). Ventrites I-VI emarginated and depressed at center, depression becoming wider from the basal ventrite to apical ventrite. Ventrites I-III densely punctate, pubescent within the depression more abundant and longer than at the sides. Male genitalia with parameres and penis guide strongly wide; penis guide as long as parameres, wider at middle, symmetrical, apex rounded (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 37–40" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figures 37 - 40. Brachiacantha aperta, male genitalia 37 Penis 38 Penis apex 39 Tegmen, lateral view 40 Tegmen." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures37-40" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520874" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">40</figureCitation>
); parameres wide, apex rounded, slightly tuberculated in the concave side margin, with abundant setae at apex and the convex margin, weakly curved (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 37–40" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figures 37 - 40. Brachiacantha aperta, male genitalia 37 Penis 38 Penis apex 39 Tegmen, lateral view 40 Tegmen." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures37-40" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520874" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">39</figureCitation>
); penis with lateral slender alae at apex (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 37–40" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figures 37 - 40. Brachiacantha aperta, male genitalia 37 Penis 38 Penis apex 39 Tegmen, lateral view 40 Tegmen." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures37-40" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520874" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">38</figureCitation>
), basal capsule not crested, inner arm slender and long, apex spender and long (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 37–40" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figures 37 - 40. Brachiacantha aperta, male genitalia 37 Penis 38 Penis apex 39 Tegmen, lateral view 40 Tegmen." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures37-40" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520874" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">37</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
